to invade America.

1:05:37.771 --> 1:05:38.897
In print, there.

1:05:39.064 --> 1:05:40.691
So, when President Wilson sees this,

1:05:40.774 --> 1:05:42.317
then he has no choice, but...

1:05:43.068 --> 1:05:44.278
He has to enter the war.

1:05:44.444 --> 1:05:46.238
